args: You're a tough one, all right!\n...Wait, what theâ€”
You can regenerate in a flash, huh?\nNothing a few extra punches won't fix!
Rrgh, dammit! I see what Bauer meant\nwhen he said this thing had me beat.
Its attacks and defense are nothing special,\nbut it heals so quickly my attacks are\nineffective. I can't keep this up forever...

There's no point in conserving my stamina.
I've gotta end it fast. One big hit, with
everything I've got!
HAAAAAAA!
There was only ever gonna be one victor,\nbub. Now, become proof of my strength!
Nothing, really. I'm just here to get\nmy revenge on the Syndicate.
I'd hoped to destroy their hideout here,\nbut it looks like someone beat me to it.
Heh... You snooze you lose!\nHa haâ€”ngh!
Big words, from someone in your state.\nWhy not just let your power run free,\nlike you did before?
Hah! You don't know what you're saying...
My arm is even more juiced up than last\ntime. If I let it loose, everything around\nme will be gone.
You would throw your life away for the\nsake of the surrounding villages?
Who said I was dying? I'mâ€”rrgh!\nI'm the strongest, stupid...
...You helped me before, so I'll do the\nsame for you.
Unleash your mana at me.\nAll of it.
Hah! *pant* You idiot. I'd blow you away.
Don't underestimate my strength.\nNow, do it!
*pant* *pant* You've got quite the\nreckless streak... Ha ha...
Aaaaand here come the rats.\nWhen you see one, you know\nthere's 30 more coming!
Do you want half? Or would you rather\nsit back and marvel at my power?
Don't go gettin' cocky.\nI'm ready to rumble.
Let them taste my dragon's strength!\nWyrmbinding!
I'll show you who's number one!\nRenegade Queen!
...Well, that's that. I don't think I'll\nbe seeing any more of my ï¼‚siblingsï¼‚\nafter this.
Which just leaves you. And we have a\nscore to settle. It's time to prove\nwho's the strongest.
I said no. You're no longer part of the\nSyndicate. We have no reason to fight.
Where the hell's this comin' from?!
I reserve my rage for the Syndicate.\nFighting you would accomplish nothing.
I spotted a squad of Syndicate soldiers\nheading north. Bauer was with them!
Then we know where we're heading.
Of course. I can't just let him crawl back\nunder whatever rock he came from.
Will you come with us to hunt Bauer?\nOr is your mind still set on battle?
I won't fight you here and now, but if you\nreally want to measure your might against\nmine, visit the Halidom, in the Mistholt.
You're free now, Bellina. You can forge\nyour own future. And the Halidom is a\ngreat place to start.
Ha ha! Bauer kept trying to make it sound\noh-so-complicated, but it's simple in\nthe end.
Guess I'm on the run now too, huh?\nMaybe I WILL stop by the Halidom...
...and prove that I'm the strongest there!\nFor now, I have ultimate freedom!
